#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.str.count.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.str.count"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:1
msgid "Count occurrences of pattern in each string of the Series/Index."
msgstr "计算 Series/Index 中每个字符串中模式出现的次数。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:3
msgid ""
"This function is used to count the number of times a particular regex "
"pattern is repeated in each of the string elements of the "
":class:`~pandas.Series`."
msgstr ""
"此函数用于计算特定正则表达式模式在 :class:`~pandas.Series` 的每个字符串"
"元素中重复的次数。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:7
msgid "Valid regular expression."
msgstr "有效的正则表达式。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:9
msgid ""
"Flags for the `re` module. For a complete list, `see here "
"<https://docs.python.org/3/howto/regex.html#compilation-flags>`_."
msgstr ""
"`re` 模块的标志。完整列表请参见 <https://docs.python.org/3/howto/regex."
"html#compilation-flags>`_。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:12
msgid "For compatibility with other string methods. Not used."
msgstr "为了与其他字符串方法兼容。未使用。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:14
msgid "Same type as the calling object containing the integer counts."
msgstr "与调用对象类型相同，包含整数计数。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:19
msgid ":py:obj:`re`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:20
msgid "Standard library module for regular expressions."
msgstr "用于正则表达式的标准库模块。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:22
msgid ":py:obj:`str.count`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:23
msgid "Standard library version, without regular expression support."
msgstr "标准库版本，不支持正则表达式。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:26
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:27
msgid ""
"Some characters need to be escaped when passing in `pat`. eg. ``'$'`` has"
" a special meaning in regex and must be escaped when finding this literal"
" character."
msgstr ""
"传入 `pat` 时，某些字符需要转义。例如，``'$'`` 在正则表达式中有特殊含义，"
"查找该字面字符时必须转义。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:32
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:46
msgid "Escape ``'$'`` to find the literal dollar sign."
msgstr "转义 ``'$'`` 以查找字面美元符号。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.count:58
msgid "This is also available on Index"
msgstr "这在 Index 上也可用"

